\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-valuenow=\"0\" aria-valuemin=\"0\" aria-valuemax=\"1\" class=\"shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" class=\"stroke-current/25\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-dasharray=\"69.11503837897544\" stroke-dashoffset=\"69.11503837897544\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" transform=\"rotate(-90 12 12)\" class=\"transition-all\"></circle></svg><span class=\"grid flex-1 *:my-auto *:row-start-1 *:col-start-1\"><span class=\"truncate transition-[opacity,translate,color]\">Team Management</span><span class=\"truncate transition-[opacity,translate] opacity-0 translate-y-full pointer-events-none\"></span></span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down shrink-0 transition-transform mx-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><div data-state=\"closed\" id=\"radix-_R_1av5u9flb_\" hidden=\"\" data-toc-popover-content=\"\" class=\"overflow-hidden\"></div></header></div><article id=\"nd-page\" data-full=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col w-full max-w-[900px] mx-auto [grid-area:main] px-4 py-6 gap-4 md:px-6 md:pt-8 xl:px-8 xl:pt-14 xl:layout:[--fd-toc-width:268px]\"><h1 class=\"text-[1.75em] font-semibold\">Team Management</h1><p class=\"text-lg text-fd-muted-foreground mb-0\">Add staff, set their schedules, and control what they can access</p><div class=\"flex flex-row gap-2 items-center border-b pb-6\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md p-2 font-medium transition-colors duration-100 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-fd-ring border bg-fd-secondary text-fd-secondary-foreground hover:bg-fd-accent hover:text-fd-accent-foreground px-2 py-1.5 text-xs gap-2 [&amp;_svg]:size-3.5 [&amp;_svg]:text-fd-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-copy\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"14\" x=\"8\" y=\"8\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2\"></path></svg>Copy Markdown</button><button type=\"button\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"radix-_R_9qav5u9flb_\" data-state=\"closed\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md p-2 font-medium transition-colors duration-100 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-fd-ring border bg-fd-secondary text-fd-secondary-foreground hover:bg-fd-accent hover:text-fd-accent-foreground px-2 py-1.5 text-xs gap-2 data-[state=open]:bg-fd-accent data-[state=open]:text-fd-accent-foreground\">Open<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down size-3.5 text-fd-muted-foreground\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"prose flex-1\"><p>The Team Management page is where you manage everyone who works at your salon — their profiles, working hours, service permissions, and login accounts.</p>\n<p>Click <strong>Team</strong> in the left menu to get started. The page is divided into two sections: <strong>Team Members</strong> and <strong>Authenticated Users</strong>.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"team-members\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#team-members\" class=\"peer\">Team Members</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Team Members are the staff profiles that appear on the Calendar. Each card shows the staff member&#x27;s photo (or initials if no photo is set), their email, and phone number.</p>\n<p>Each card has three action buttons:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Edit Shift</strong> — set their weekly working hours</li>\n<li><strong>Edit</strong> — update their profile details</li>\n<li><strong>Delete</strong> (red trash icon) — remove them permanently</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To view archived staff, toggle <strong>Show archived team members only</strong> in the top right corner.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"adding-a-team-member\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#adding-a-team-member\" class=\"peer\">Adding a team member</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Click <strong>+ Add → Add Team Member</strong>. A form will pop up.</p>\n<div class=\"fd-steps\"><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click the <strong>+</strong> circle at the top to upload a profile photo (JPEG or PNG, under 2 MB). This is optional but recommended — it helps identify staff on the Calendar.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Enter their <strong>First Name</strong> (required) and <strong>Last Name</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Set a <strong>Calendar Color</strong> — this is the color used for their column on the Calendar. Each staff member should have a distinct color to make them easy to tell apart.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Optionally enter a <strong>Team Member ID</strong> — useful if your business uses internal staff ID numbers.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Set <strong>Category Permissions</strong> — toggle on the service categories this staff member is allowed to perform (e.g., Hair, Nails, Facial). All categories are enabled by default. Staff will only appear as a booking option for the categories you enable.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Toggle <strong>Visible to Clients</strong> on if this staff member should appear in client-facing booking. This is on by default.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Toggle <strong>Admin User</strong> on if they need full access to the system (Reports, Settings, Commission, Dashboard). Off by default.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Select a <strong>Location</strong> (required).</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click <strong>Add Team Member</strong>.</p></div></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"editing-a-team-member\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#editing-a-team-member\" class=\"peer\">Editing a team member</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Click <strong>Edit</strong> on any team member card to update their photo, name, calendar color, category permissions, admin status, or location.</p>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2 my-4 rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-3 ps-1 text-sm text-fd-card-foreground shadow-md\" style=\"--callout-color:var(--color-fd-warning, var(--color-fd-muted))\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"w-0.5 bg-(--callout-color)/50 rounded-sm\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert size-5 -me-0.5 fill-(--callout-color) text-fd-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"><p>You cannot remove admin access from the last remaining admin. Make sure at least one other admin exists before making that change.</p></div></div></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"setting-working-hours-edit-shift\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#setting-working-hours-edit-shift\" class=\"peer\">Setting working hours (Edit Shift)</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Each staff member can have their own weekly schedule so the Calendar only shows them as available when they&#x27;re actually working.</p>\n<div class=\"fd-steps\"><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click <strong>Edit Shift</strong> on the team member&#x27;s card.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>For each day of the week, set their <strong>start</strong> and <strong>finish time</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Mark any day as <strong>Off</strong> if they don&#x27;t work that day.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click <strong>Save</strong>.</p></div></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"authenticated-users\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#authenticated-users\" class=\"peer\">Authenticated Users</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>The <strong>Authenticated Users</strong> section sits below the team member grid and shows all staff login accounts. These cards have an <strong>orange border</strong> to distinguish them from team member profiles.</p>\n<p>Each card shows the user&#x27;s name, their <strong>Auth User</strong> label, email address, and Location ID.</p>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2 my-4 rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-3 ps-1 text-sm text-fd-card-foreground shadow-md\" style=\"--callout-color:var(--color-fd-info, var(--color-fd-muted))\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"w-0.5 bg-(--callout-color)/50 rounded-sm\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-info size-5 -me-0.5 fill-(--callout-color) text-fd-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 16v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h.01\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"><p>A team member profile and a login account are two separate things. A team member profile controls how someone appears on the Calendar. A login account controls how they log in to NxCut. Most staff will need both.</p></div></div></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"adding-a-login-account-auth-user\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#adding-a-login-account-auth-user\" class=\"peer\">Adding a login account (Auth User)</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Click <strong>+ Add → Add Auth User</strong>. A form will pop up.</p>\n<div class=\"fd-steps\"><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Enter their <strong>Email</strong> (required) — this will be their username when logging in.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Set a <strong>Password</strong> (required).</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Optionally enter a <strong>Display Name</strong> and <strong>Phone Number</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Toggle <strong>Admin User</strong> on if they should have full system access.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Select a <strong>Location</strong> (required).</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click <strong>Create User</strong>. The account is active immediately.</p></div></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"archiving-a-team-member\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#archiving-a-team-member\" class=\"peer\">Archiving a team member</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>If someone leaves but you want to keep their history in the system, archive them instead of deleting.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Open their profile and choose <strong>Archive</strong>.</li>\n<li>Archived members are hidden from the default view.</li>\n<li>Toggle <strong>Show archived team members only</strong> at the top of the page to find them again.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"quick-reference\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#quick-reference\" class=\"peer\">Quick reference</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Feature</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Profile photo</td><td>JPEG or PNG, max 2 MB</td></tr><tr><td>Calendar color</td><td>Makes each staff member&#x27;s column easy to identify</td></tr><tr><td>Team Member ID</td><td>Optional internal staff ID number</td></tr><tr><td>Category permissions</td><td>Per-category toggles — controls which services they can be booked for</td></tr><tr><td>Working hours</td><td>Set per staff member, per day of the week</td></tr><tr><td>Auth users</td><td>Separate login accounts shown with an orange border</td></tr><tr><td>Admin access</td><td>Grants full access to Reports, Settings, Commission, and Dashboard</td></tr><tr><td>Visible to clients</td><td>Controls whether they appear in client-facing booking</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"@container grid gap-4 grid-cols-2\"><a class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border p-4 text-sm transition-colors hover:bg-fd-accent/80 hover:text-fd-accent-foreground @max-lg:col-span-full\" href=\"/docs/clients\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-left -mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15 18-6-6 6-6\"></path></svg><p>Clients</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">Manage your client database — add, search, and view full client profiles</p></a><a class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border p-4 text-sm transition-colors hover:bg-fd-accent/80 hover:text-fd-accent-foreground @max-lg:col-span-full text-end\" href=\"/docs/commission\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium flex-row-reverse\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right -mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><p>Commission</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">Set up commission rules for your staff and generate detailed salary slips</p></a></div></article><div id=\"nd-toc\" class=\"sticky top-(--fd-docs-row-1) h-[calc(var(--fd-docs-height)-var(--fd-docs-row-1))] flex flex-col [grid-area:toc] w-(--fd-toc-width) pt-12 pe-4 pb-2 max-xl:hidden\"><h3 id=\"toc-title\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-text-align-start size-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21 5H3\"></path><path d=\"M15 12H3\"></path><path d=\"M17 19H3\"></path></svg>On this page</h3><div class=\"relative min-h-0 text-sm ms-px overflow-auto [scrollbar-width:none] mask-[linear-gradient(to_bottom,transparent,white_16px,white_calc(100%-16px),transparent)] py-3\"><div class=\"relative\"><div data-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-y-0 inset-s-0 bg-fd-primary w-px transition-[clip-path]\" style=\"clip-path:polygon(0 var(--fd-top), 100% var(--fd-top), 100% calc(var(--fd-top) + var(--fd-height)), 0 calc(var(--fd-top) + var(--fd-height)))\"></div><div class=\"flex flex-col border-s border-fd-foreground/10\"><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#team-members\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Team Members</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#adding-a-team-member\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Adding a team member</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#editing-a-team-member\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-